            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.81

- 支持在编辑过程中拖动截图区域的四边和四角。
- 选区最大可扩展到当前屏幕边界。
- 调整时同步更新遮罩、工具栏、标注位置及最终输出范围。

---

- Added resizable capture bounds during editing.
- Drag any edge or corner up to the current display boundary.
- Keeps the mask, toolbar, annotations, and final output synchronized.
